AddHandler mod_python .py
PythonHandler submerge
PythonOption SubmergeEnv /home/avaeq/public_html/submerge/submerge.conf
PythonAutoReload on
PythonDebug On

### RewriteRules ###
RewriteEngine on
RewriteBase     /path/to/www/dir/ # don't forget the trailing /

RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f
RewriteRule ^(.*)$ submerge.py/$1

RewriteRule ^/?$ submerge.py

AuthUserFile /usr/local/submerge/.htpasswd
AuthType Basic
AuthName "Submerge"
Require valid-user
